about 41000 up from 33000 
the nurses were seeking raises of 16 percent in the first year 
and 14 percent in the second managements offer amounts to 235 
percent over two years 
also at issue in the talks is the companys practice of cutting 
nurses hours when there are few patients in the hospital the 
nurses are seeking contract provisions to protect their income 
