the b2 stealth bomber sped down a runway 
thursday successfully completing its final ground test and setting 
the stage for a first flight that could come as early as saturday 
an air force general said 
the sleek batwinged bomber raced down the runway at air force 
plant 42 achieving a top speed of 75 mph said brig gen richard 
